name: Sylvia's Bowl of Lemons
description: Lemons were a major recurring theme in Sylvia’s later life. Her last words on social media were “Life gave me lemons, the lemonade made me rich.” To her friends and followers, lemons came to symbolize her journey. She made the most of her lifetime: making a positive impact on people, cultivating deep friendships, leading a fulfilling career, and accomplishing her goal of writing a book.
